### Higher-Frequency Complement Research（Orchestrator → Alpha Researcher）
- 啟動 `higher_freq_complement` research task（`tasks/active/20260325_163400_higher_freq_complement.yaml`）
- Portfolio Strategist 診斷：1h trend-following 在 chop regime 虧損 + feedback loop 太慢（~2-5 trades/week）
- 測試 3 個候選方向：
  1. **15m MR Liquidity Sweep → FAIL**：gross exp 全數為負（BTC -0.002, ETH -0.002, SOL -0.004），MR Iron Rule violated，WR 僅 26-29%。Crypto positive skew 結構性殺死 absolute price MR（`scripts/research/mr_liquidity_15m_feasibility.py`、`config/research_mr_liquidity_15m.yaml`）
  2. **15m TSMOM Rescaled → FAIL**：~15K trades/yr（成本太高），corr(prod)=0.63-0.82（無分散化價值），avg SR=0.26 勉強正（`scripts/research/tsmom_15m_feasibility.py`、`config/research_tsmom_15m.yaml`）
  3. **Crypto Pair Spread z-score → WEAK GO**：BTC/ETH, BTC/SOL, ETH/SOL log-spread。IC(z_168h→24h)=+0.035~0.057，所有 z-score threshold 皆正 gross exp。BTC/ETH z2.0: 234 tr/yr, WR=38%, gross_exp=+0.007。需 hedged cost-adjusted backtest（`scripts/research/pair_spread_eda.py`）
- **結論**：Pair spread 是唯一可行的 higher-frequency 方向。HANDOFF → @quant-developer 實作 pair spread strategy + proper cost modeling
